title: Microsoft Windows XP Professional Corporate Edition Version 2002
description:
Windows XP Professional Corporate Edition 2002

This version of Windows XP requires no activation and has not been tampered with since it was copied from the Corporate Disc.

I am using it on 10 Machines seamlessly with the same serial. No problems at all.

NOTE: Sometimes Microsoft Software such as the newer media player (10 and above) that has anti-piracy built into them can detect the Windows XP installation as pirated. There is no escaping this if it occurs but to re-format an reload Windows. Generally this isn't a problem
